  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > “愿尽知之，惟尔所择；睖睁之地，静候君来。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身为民俗杂志编辑的边承林收到了诡异的四段拓片，循着拓片上的诗词线索，来到了一个隐藏在大山深处的神秘村庄——睖（lèng）睁（zhēng）村。可他未曾想到的是，这一趟旅程，竟牵扯到了村庄里几十年前的数桩命案，这四张不知是何人寄给他的拓片，其中也隐藏着关于他自身的秘密，随着他调查的深入，真相也在逐渐浮出水面……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遗魂村志，诡谲仪式</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在村庄住下后，你发现了一册 “遗魂村志”，其中记载的故事一个比一个匪夷所思，吃人老鼠，纸人新娘，血色村庄……这些故事或许并非只是故事，它们与村庄里埋藏多年的秘密紧密相连。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >村庄的【镇灵日】即将到来，村中的气氛越发令人不安，友善的村民似乎在隐瞒着什么、计划着什么，你可以相信谁？</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819030/extras/becdf35524c3f57ce9b14ed2ed7099a9.avif?t=1759031203\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819030/extras_big/becdf35524c3f57ce9b14ed2ed7099a9.avif?t=1759031203 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>双重探索，缜密推理</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 玩家一方面以第一人称的视角亲历村志中“鬼”故事，另一方面回到现实以主人公的身份在村庄收集各种线索。在故事记载的伪装和现实村民的隐瞒之下，在虚实交错中拼凑出真相的原貌。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用游戏中的【推理笔记本】，整理“鬼”故事中和现实中搜集到的线索。你还可以使用手机求助其他杂志社成员，获得更多信息，提高故事还原度。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819030/extras/62e1245e5f75147631503f4ad2d6a0d5.poster.avif?t=1759031203\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819030/extras/62e1245e5f75147631503f4ad2d6a0d5.webm?t=1759031203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819030/extras/62e1245e5f75147631503f4ad2d6a0d5.mp4?t=1759031203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>独特美术，沉浸解谜</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏采用了多种独特的美术风格，暗黑背景的粗线条简笔画、扭曲变形的场景、奇瑰的色彩，每个“鬼”故事的美术风格与故事内容本身一样诡异，营造出悬疑、不安的氛围。你能否穿透扭曲、夸张的场景，接近真相？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > “鬼”故事解谜和现实探索紧密结合，让游戏体验更加丰富。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819030/extras/cc4a6c6f7bef2e86b12cd96752e7632c.poster.avif?t=1759031203\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819030/extras/cc4a6c6f7bef2e86b12cd96752e7632c.webm?t=1759031203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819030/extras/cc4a6c6f7bef2e86b12cd96752e7632c.mp4?t=1759031203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
